name: Roller Coaster of Wonders
description:
From a flea market VHS discovery to Reddit's amusement parks subgroups. It was a privilege being able to explore this amazing universe and discover some stunning rides in different parts of the globe. 

This is the final piece of this amazing journey. 

Thanks to everyone who kept up with this project during these past few weeks (:
